channel.title: Somebody help me with this!
channel.description:

And I get this error when I compile:
[code]src\server\model\objects\Doors.java:115: cannot find symbol symbol : class Objects location: class server.model.players.objects.Doors Objects o = new Objects(-1, d.doorX, d.doorY, d.doorZ, 0 , d.type, 0); ^ src\server\model\objects\Doors.java:115: cannot find symbol symbol : class Objects location: class server.model.players.objects.Doors Objects o = new Objects(-1, d.doorX, d.doorY, d.doorZ, 0 , d.type, 0); ^ src\server\model\objects\Doors.java:122: cannot find symbol symbol : class Objects location: class server.model.players.objects.Doors Objects o = new Objects(-1, d.doorX, d.doorY, d.doorZ, 0 , d.type, 0); ^ src\server\model\objects\Doors.java:122: cannot find symbol symbol : class Objects location: class server.model.players.objects.Doors Objects o = new Objects(-1, d.doorX, d.doorY, d.doorZ, 0 , d.type, 0); ^ src\server\model\objects\Doors.java:140: cannot find symbol symbol : class Objects location: class server.model.players.objects.Doors Server.objectHandler.placeObject(new Objects(d.doorId, d.doorX, d.doorY, d.doorZ, getNextFace(d), d.type, 0)); ^ 5 errors Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
